# Public Assets Directory

This directory contains public assets for the AI Agent Sandbox project:

- Logo and branding images
- Screenshots and demo images
- Documentation images
- Marketing materials

## Directory Structure

```
public/
├── logo/           # Company and product logos
├── screenshots/    # Application screenshots
├── docs/          # Documentation images
├── marketing/     # Marketing materials
└── .gitkeep       # Keep this directory in git
```

## Usage

Images in this directory are served directly by web servers and can be referenced in:

- README.md files
- Documentation
- Web applications
- Marketing materials

## Guidelines

- Use optimized images (WebP, AVIF when possible)
- Include alt text for accessibility
- Use descriptive filenames
- Keep file sizes reasonable (<500KB per image)
- Use consistent naming conventions